of the nutrition shot,

00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:43,100
I'll be able
to do that already.

00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:45,260
The $75,000 that you give me

00:39:45,260 --> 00:39:46,900
will just be so that there's
not a backlog.

00:39:49,660 --> 00:39:52,060
Unfortunately, I've invested

00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:55,430
in similar products that would
compete against this.

00:39:55,430 --> 00:39:56,700
I'm out.

00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:59,260
Understood. Thank you.
I appreciate your time.

00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:03,900
Robert, I think you have
a compelling story.

00:40:03,900 --> 00:40:07,730
And who wouldn't
fall in love with you?

00:40:07,730 --> 00:40:09,400
I'm in love with you.

00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:11,200
I'm a little in love
with you, too.

00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:12,700
